nodes.text: Headhunter Four was the callsign used by Jessa Vandangante's wingman when flying with Headhunter Flight during the Battle of the Outlaw Tech Base, in 2 BBY. He was a member of the Vandangante outlaw techs and was a gray-skinned humanoid from the planet Lafra. He had over four minutes of actual combat time prior to the battle.
